name: BE WILD
description: BE WILD is one of those works that really encapsulates the feeling of journeying alone in the middle of a thick forest; lost among the towering sentinels of the woods. Walking and talking with the ancient secrets and wisdom of the indigenous peoples of this bountiful land. It is a privilege and an honor to be allowed here and welcomed by my life partner's community. The thicket of timber is an oasis of solace on the Tsuut'ina First Nation.
